<plot>A two-timing bigamist, played by Chow Yun-Fat, finds himself concocting scheme after scheme with his best friend, Waise Lee Chi Hung, to prevent either of his wives from discovering his bigamy. The unwanted intervention of a police officer (Kent Cheng) as well as a series of unfortunate events lead to the wives (Joey Wong, Sally Yeh) discovery of the whole plot. They team up with Chi Hung's exasperated fiancee, Carrie Ng Ka Lai, to exact revenge upon the two men.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?123683</url></doc>
